16 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
17 SECTION 1. NEW LAW A new section of law to be codified
18 in the Oklahoma Statutes as Section 509A of Title 57, unless there
19 is created a duplication in numbering, reads as follows:
20 There is hereby created in the State Treasury a revolving fund
21 for the Department of Corrections to be designated the "Prison
22 Acquisition Revolving Fund". The fund shall be a continuing fund,
23 not subject to fiscal year limitations, and shall consist of all
24 monies designated for deposit by law. All monies accruing to the
